Operation Close The Pool
{{needsmoar|Pictures of raid and Information}}
<br>
In late July [[Anonymous|anon]] noticed a news story. An ugly [[fat]] [[bitch]], AKA [[Mary Alice Altorfer]], saw a [[Pools Closed]] banner on her subdivision pool and cried "racism" to the press. Anon saw this as yet another opportunity to star on [[Fox News|faux news]] and create much bawwwwing resulting in epic lulz. On July 18th, [[/b/tards]] went out early in the morning and closed many pools nationwide to commemorate the lulz that had happened with [[Mary Alice Altorfer]] hoping to recreate a similar scenario but nationwide. Anon has yet to decide on another date to raid the pools, but until then...happy closing!  

'''[[TL;DR]]: Close every single fucking pool that you live by nao!'''

